  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> </font><b>O lord\n        thou pluckest ...</b><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p>From St. Augustine's <i>Confessions </i>again. The\n        collocation of these two representatives of eastern and\n        western asceticism, as the culmination of this part of\n        the poem, is not an accident. [Eliot's note]</p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td> </td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Waste_A.htm\"><font>back to \"The Waste Land\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
